00:02:41.170 --> 00:02:44.700
And they're mostly
Canadian, if not all Canadian

00:02:44.700 --> 00:02:46.590
and definitely all based in Canada.

00:02:46.590 --> 00:02:48.710
And Kati, is also Canadian,
which is really great

00:02:48.710 --> 00:02:51.120
