heard of from Canada and listened

00:09:23.970 --> 00:09:26.210
to their works and Kati was
one of the four that really

00:09:26.210 --> 00:09:28.570
that really jumped out to
us as just really strong

00:09:28.570 --> 00:09:33.460
and we really just felt
connected to what she was writing.

00:09:33.460 --> 00:09:36.410
